      "text": "<details>\n<summary>text_image</summary>\n\nProcess 1\nacquire(&p->lock);\n...\np->state = RUNNABLE;\nswtch(&p->context, ...);\n\n    swtch(...); // return\n    release(&p->lock);\n\n        // find a RUNNABLE p\n\n    acquire(&p->lock);\n    p->state = RUNNING;\n    swtch(...,&p->context);\n\n            swtch(&p->context,...); // return\n    release(&p->lock);\n</details>",
